    {
      "id": "el_8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 258,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Total Work = LCM of all days\nEfficiency = Total Work / Days\nTime = Total Work / Combined Eff\n\n     (LCM)\n       |\n  -----+-----\n Eff(A)    Eff(B)\n = LCM/a   = LCM/b\n\nWages → split by efficiency ratio",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
