    {
      "id": "el_17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 242,
      "height": 125,
      "text": "SI = P × R × T / 100\nA = P + SI = P(1 + RT/100)\n\nCI: A = P(1 + R/100)^T\nCI = A - P\n\nCI - SI (2 yrs) = P(R/100)²\nRule of 72: doubles in 72/R yrs",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
