    {
      "id": "el_20",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 258,
      "height": 125,
      "text": "a:b = c:d → ad = bc\nMean proportional = √(a×b)\nThird proportional = b²/a\n\nDirect: more→more (×)\nInverse: more→less (÷)\n\nAlligation: (d₂-m)/(m-d₁) = q₁/q₂",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
