      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "a:b = c:d → ad = bc\nMean proportional = √(a×b)\nThird proportional = b²/a\n\nDirect: more→more (×)\nInverse: more→less (÷)\n\nAlligation: (d₂-m)/(m-d₁) = q₁/q₂",
