    {
      "id": "el_23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 572,
      "width": 211,
      "height": 125,
      "text": "Avg = Sum / n\nSum = Avg × n\n\nAvg of 1 to n = (n+1)/2\nAvg of first n even = (n+1)\nAvg of first n odd = n\n\nWeighted Avg = Σwᵢxᵢ / Σwᵢ",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
