      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 572,
      "width": 266,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Downstream = B + S (with current)\nUpstream = B - S (against current)\n\nB = (Down + Up) / 2\nS = (Down - Up) / 2\n\nAvg round trip = (B²-S²)/B",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
