      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 973,
      "width": 258,
      "height": 94,
      "text": "nPr = n!/(n-r)!  (order matters)\nnCr = n!/r!(n-r)! (order doesn't)\n\nP(E) = favorable / total\nP(A∪B) = P(A)+P(B)-P(A∩B)\nP(not A) = 1 - P(A)",
