      "height": 125,
      "text": "HCF × LCM = Product of 2 numbers\nLCM of fracs = LCM(num)/HCF(den)\n\nUnit digit cycles: period 4\n2→2,4,8,6  3→3,9,7,1\n7→7,9,3,1  8→8,4,2,6\n\nDivisibility: 3→digit sum, 4→last 2",
